name: Kali’s Merkin
description: Even time, creation, destruction and power need a pubic toupee sometimes. Behold Kali’s Merkin! An astral hairpiece for the most majestic of gates. The second collaboration between Mario Klingemann (@Quasimondo) and James Paterson (@Presstube), this time with aural accompaniment from Stephen Ramsay (@YoungGalaxy).
